'''Joy Nunieh''' yin whẹyidọtọ po anadenanutọ dai tọn na Niger Delta Development Commission.
E yin alọhẹndotena to azọn mẹ to Azan fọtọn-nukun-ẹnẹtọ, Afínplọsun, Owhe 2020 tọn mẹ gbọn Togan Buhari dali bo yi Kemebradikumo Pondei dó diọtẹn na ẹn to afọdopolọji.
Nunieh tin to nujijọ yinkọ-hẹngblenamẹ tọn NDDC tọn he zọnbọ ye sawhẹdokọna Goodswill Akpabio.
